These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: canasta, bridge, go
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, metal, country
1. the person playing bridge is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the fan of indie##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Game          | canasta      | bridge        | go     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Music-Genre         | indie  | metal      | country    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
House: colonial, cottage, farmhouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
There 3 different types of food: kale, apricot, pumpkin
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person eating kale##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the cottage house##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
6. the farmhouse house is in an even position##4
7. the person eating pumpkin is between the person watching disaster movies and the colonial house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| House           | cottage    | farmhouse | colonial |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| Pet           | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret     |
| Food         | apricot | pumpkin       | kale   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cranberry, watermelon
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, ambient, gospel
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, march, december
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, train
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the person driving the train##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
4. the person eating carrot is between the fan of ambient and the person driving the train##2
5. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | carrot | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | funk | ambient |
| Birthday           | march       | july   | december    |
| Transport     | train      | bike   | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, august
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, folk
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the fan of metal##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | photography  | chess       | woodworking |
| Birthday           | august     | may      | june   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | ambient | folk     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

