.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, handball, cycling
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, baking
There are 3 different nationalities: german, mexican, polish
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the german##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the polish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Sport           | skateboarding | handball | cycling |
| Hobby   | baking      | hiking   | rock-climbing            |
| Nationality   | mexican   | polish  | german         |

