.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, photographer, social-worker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, electronic, rock
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, sunflower, daisy
1. the fan of electronic is between the photographer and the person eating cauliflower##2
2. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the fan of rock is the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Food          | raspberry    | asparagus     | cauliflower |
| Job           | photographer | social-worker | doctor      |
| Music-Genre   | rock      | electronic       | folk    |
| Flower   | sunflower      | daffodil         | daisy     |

