The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, zombie
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, orchid, rose
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, july, september
1. the person eating blueberry is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person eating orange is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person eating garlic##2
7. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Food          | garlic | blueberry | orange |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action    | zombie |
| Flower   | orchid  | bellflower   | rose    |
| Birthday     | september   | january       | july |

