.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, march, november
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, dancing, sudoku
There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, russian
House: victorian, gothic-revival, modern
1. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the pakistani and the modern house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Birthday      | march | september    | november  |
| Hobby         | sudoku        | camping   | dancing   |
| Nationality   | russian       | german    | pakistani |
| House     | modern          | gothic-revival | victorian       |

