3. the turkish is the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the turkish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage          | sprite  | soy-milk   | water      |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | punk      | blues      |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian | turkish    |
| City           | new-york   | prague     | marseilles |

