.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, black, light-blue
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish, hamster
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, thai
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, van
1. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the thai##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Color           | apricot     | light-blue    | black |
| Pet   | guinea-pig  | fish | hamster      |
| Nationality   | thai       | japanese   | chinese    |
| Transport     | snowmobile | van        | roller     |

