2. the person who growsorchid is the brazilian##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who growspoppy is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Game      | poker     | chess      | billiard  |
