.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, tea
City: miami, nizza, boston
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, motorbike, van
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | tea       | soy-milk   | iced-tea |
| City   | miami | boston     | nizza |
| Transport           | ship      | motorbike | van    |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | soccer     | biathlon |

