3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating lettuce##1
5. the modern house is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the airplane is the tower house##1
7. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating cranberry is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Food          | cranberry  | apricot   | lettuce |
| Transport   | scooter      | motorbike      | airplane   |
| House   | futuristic     | modern | tower |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket   | rugby   |

