.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, puzzles, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, rock
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, mouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, drama, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Hobby           | baking  | magic-tricks | puzzles   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock           | disco      |
| Pet           | mouse   | horse          | guinea-pig |
| Movie-Genre     | musical    | scientific           | drama |

 